like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:32:45.000Z","msg":"真正看破紅塵會唔會仲喺連登扮陶淵明？上山吸風飲露，俗世唔適合你久留。<br />\n<br />\n其實假膠味幾濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4d634b105d89b703a7af1ea0364d733f9a7f48","tid":383200,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"朝聞道，夕可死已。<br />\n你未死？"},{"pid":"3ff5230294ee62fbf335a6141effd1eb2410ef2d","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朝聞道，夕可死已。<br />\n你未死？</blockquote><br />\n點解D有智慧既人都會自殺? <br />\n唔洗講例子啦 <br />\n不過我唔同D ON9為情自殺個DON9仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係睇清楚呢個世界先自殺"},{"pid":"6e887c16fc5aef8fa8c0063b6f1feeba971c3af1","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"其實我諗呢 <br />\n係唔係因為人有思想，咁就會有唔同既意見 <br />\n咁每人都唔想否認自己係錯，又想拎自己套加於別人上 <br />\n想人認同佢 <br />\n咁矛盾，對錯就產生 <br />\n其實係咪對錯冇標準，只要自己認為係就係？ <br />\n咁道應該係最接近對錯，最好就無欲無求無知"},{"pid":"7ba5c8f802b7f5355accbd8c1fad4ee55250489f","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真正看破紅塵會唔會仲喺連登扮陶淵明？上山吸風飲露，俗世唔適合你久留。<br />\n<br />\n其實假膠味幾濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又冇話唔面對現實，不過係看破咁去面對姐，根本 <br />\n個個就曲解哂我意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e220a51383c8ae4d026909627402c35817d20d78","tid":383200,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>16號經歷過啲咩 咁快就看破紅塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解做乜野一定要年紀大先係岩? <br />\n我已經睇左好多哲學書,道,佛,已經拎哂佢地D精華 <br />\n佢地加埋幾千歲,我認佢地係人生經驗個D多又經過好多野 <br />\n先領悟到,但係佢地出書都係為左話俾人聽,咁學左佢地 <br />\n咪等於有幾千年既經驗LO</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下自己講咩膠論先<br />\n學左佢地 等於幾千年經驗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我已經明白左莊子同佛陀D精華 <br />\n他們苦思多年都係為左呢D,以佢地得到領悟就教導世人 <br />\n都係想佢地早D明白,唔洗再浪費時間去思考呢D <br />\n定係你想講佢地個套唔適合呢個時代?</blockquote><br />\n建議你先去睇佛陀成道時講過咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94cad49c19d91193dedc17cd6134015eb07dd1b","tid":383200,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/383229/page/3?post=fefce24beee1c8f279123edb29d6b718c7034964\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/383229/page/3?post=fefce24beee1c8f279123edb29d6b718c7034964</a><br />\n<br />\n人地10歲看破紅塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97b666636b810dfabe70375d8cea5fc95d32ef8","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議你先去睇佛陀成道時講過咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講咁多野係咪想講面對現實，腳踏實地咁去做人"},{"pid":"bf9d4085934357787997adb09086e7f7c72c6e9d","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/383229/page/3?post=fefce24beee1c8f279123edb29d6b718c7034964\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/383229/page/3?post=fefce24beee1c8f279123edb29d6b718c7034964</a><br />\n<br />\n人地10歲看破紅塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係唔係自己想法唔好講出黎 <br />\n唔係會俾人屌柒？"},{"pid":"488c698e25d47ad89550d6a6eca46d72b512411c","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"其實係咪唔應該胡思亂想,唔好諗埋呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b21150c1fef8c28e392005451843023f942ef85","tid":383200,"uid":69753,"like":0,"disli